2026 2026
1 set for any meeting. In the case of meetings called by the administrator,
2 notice shall be provided to the clerk of the community improvement
3 district not less than seven days prior to the date set for any meeting.
4 (2) Except as provided in subsection (5) of section 84-1411, within
5 the timeframe required by subsection (3) of section 84-1413, after any
6 meeting of a community improvement district board of trustees or called
7 by the administrator, the clerk or administrator of the community
