1 the real estate shall distribute the most recent statement filed in
2 accordance with this section to any prospective purchaser of any real
3 estate located within a community improvement district.
4 (3) The real estate broker or salesperson or, if none, the owner
5 shall obtain an acknowledgment from any purchaser of any real estate
